<h2 id="潮流开源">潮流开源</h2>
<p><strong>SingleFile：保存网页成一个 html 文件</strong><br>
<a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/singlefile/mpiodijhokgodhhofbcjdecpffjipkle">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/singlefile/mpiodijhokgodhhofbcjdecpffjipkle</a><br>
